OL,3,CPassenger says hantavirus outbreak on
OL,4,Ccruise ship 'could have been prevented'
OL,6,FITV News has spoken to a passenger on
OL,7,FMV Hondius who believes the outbreak
OL,8,Fcould have been contained if
OL,9,Fsufficient precautions were in place.
OL,11,FRuhi Cenet, a Turkish national, was on
OL,12,Fboard MV Hondius for 24 days from the
OL,13,Fstart of April.
OL,15,FMidway through the expedition, the
OL,16,FCaptain gathered all passengers for a
OL,17,Fmeeting at 9am on the 12th April.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G1/8
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
