CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F311A1778205813
OL,3,CPassenger says hantavirus outbreak on
OL,4,Ccruise ship 'could have been prevented'
OL,6,F"We were told by the captain that the
OL,7,Fpassenger had died because of natural
OL,8,Fcauses and we are not in danger of any
OL,9,Fcontagious disease," Ruhi told ITV
OL,10,FNews"This relaxed us, but it was
OL,11,Fmisguiding."
OL,13,FThe body of the deceased Dutch
OL,14,Fnational stayed on board of the ship
OL,15,Ffor another 12 days until it docked in
OL,16,FSt Helena.
OL,18,FThe deceased man was travelling with
OL,19,Fhis wife, who during that time, was
OL,20,Fbeing comforted - in close proximity -
OL,21,Fby other passengers.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G2/8
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,312,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31103
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F311A1778205813
OL,3,CPassenger says hantavirus outbreak on
OL,4,Ccruise ship 'could have been prevented'
OL,6,FA few days further into the journey to
OL,7,FSt Helena, she then became symptomatic
OL,8,F- of what we now know as Hantavirus -
OL,9,Fand later died from the disease too.
OL,11,F"All of the other passengers were
OL,12,Fgiving her hugs and everyone was
OL,13,Ftalking to her.
OL,15,F"At every meal, someone else was
OL,16,Fsitting beside her and we had open
OL,17,Fbuffets, we had group activities,
OL,18,Flecture sessions, we had meetings in
OL,19,Flounge area.
OL,26,@sD@AOUwD@AOU
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G3/8
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,312,300,200,140,000,100
