CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F311A1778205813
OL,3,CPassenger says hantavirus outbreak on
OL,4,Ccruise ship 'could have been prevented'
OL,6,F"On a ship like Hondius, there isn't
OL,7,Fmuch to do other than socialising."
OL,9,FRuhi was part of the group that
OL,10,Fdisembarked at St Helena on 24th
OL,11,FApril, along with the deceased man's
OL,12,Fwife.
OL,14,FBy that time, she too had started to
OL,15,Fshow symptoms of Hantavirus.
OL,17,F"She was struggling to stand, she was
OL,18,Flooking really ill.J"We thought that
OL,19,Fshe was just having a very deep grief,
OL,20,Fbut in fact she had the virus."
OL,26,@nD@AOUoD@cO]yD@AOUzD@UOU|D@_OU
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G4/8
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
