OL,3,CPassenger says hantavirus outbreak on
OL,4,Ccruise ship 'could have been prevented'
OL,6,FSubscribe free to our weekly
OL,7,Fnewsletter for exclusive and original
OL,8,Fcoverage from ITV News. Direct to your
OL,9,Finbox every Friday morning.
OL,11,FFrom St Helena, Ruhi and the rest of
OL,12,Fthe group -including the infected
OL,13,FDutch woman - travelled together on a
OL,14,Fflight to Johannesburg, where the
OL,15,Fwoman later died.
OL,17,F"I saw her on a wheelchair and that
OL,18,Fwas unusual because she did not have
OL,19,Fany problems walking.
OL,26,@yD@AOU
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G5/8
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,312,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31106
SC,0006
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F311A1778205813
OL,3,CPassenger says hantavirus outbreak on
OL,4,Ccruise ship 'could have been prevented'
OL,6,F"Once she landed to Johannesburg, I
OL,7,Fheard that she had passed away.
OL,9,F"I didn't know the presence of the
OL,10,Fvirus while I was on board, we could
OL,11,Fhave end up having the virus in our
OL,12,Fsystem.
OL,14,F"I feel very unhappy with the ship
OL,15,Fmanagement. I wish they would have
OL,16,Fthought about it being a potential
OL,17,Fcontagious disease."
OL,26,@nD@AOUqD@AOUvD@AOUyD@TO]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G6/8
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
