OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,312,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31107
SC,0007
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F311A1778205813
OL,3,CPassenger says hantavirus outbreak on
OL,4,Ccruise ship 'could have been prevented'
OL,6,FRuhi is now self isolating at home in
OL,7,FIstanbul and is not displaying any
OL,8,Fsymptoms, but has regrets at the way
OL,9,Fthe situation was managed.
OL,11,F"I wish people were isolated well.
OL,13,F"This problem could have been
OL,14,Fprevented on the first casualty, when
OL,15,Fthe first casualty occurred.
OL,16,F"Sometimes I dream to warn people, but
OL,17,Fthere is no solution. It already
OL,18,Fhappened."
OL,26,@sD@AOUuD@AOUxD@AOUzD@JO]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G7/8
